54
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:41,780
Why?

55
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:46,460
I'm afraid they'll be injured,
and they're in the way.

56
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,140
Are you not going out ever?

57
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,660
