60
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:56,540
What should we do then?

61
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:03,060
Wait for them to leave themselves.

62
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,800
We can't give them the chance
to blame us.

63
