99
00:09:07,820 --> 00:09:10,300
We'll collect Hui Ba's body
after eating.

100
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,140
Alright.

101
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:13,700
Now?

102
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,660
